# search_irida_by_sample_name
# search all accessible IRIDA projects for a sample by sampleName
# returns all matching samples with their project context
#
# IRIDA has no search-by-name endpoint. This function iterates all accessible projects,
# fetches each project's sample list, and filters client-side by sampleName.
# Runtime scales with the total number of projects and samples visible to the token.
# Use an admin token to search all projects instance-wide.
#
# usage: search_irida_by_sample_name SAMPLE_NAME
#
# example: search_irida_by_sample_name 2017-01-545-1-1-2-1
